illery for grillicious grill fare, without ever having to deplete your home charcoal silo.</p>', '', 10.00, 5.00, 0, '2010-08-20 06:43:00', '2010-08-21 23:40:00', 50.00, 5.00, 5.00, 8, NULL, 42464, 53, '<div class="page_content clearfix">\r\n<div class="article description">\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><a href="http://bit.ly/abqkoF">TripAdvisors</a> give Two Rows Classic Grille an average of 3.5 owl eyes. <a href="http://bit.ly/9MGoHI">Yelpers</a> give the restaurant a 3.5-star average, and five <a href="http://bit.ly/cLd4gC">Insider Pagers</a> give the it a three-star average:</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The gourmet brick oven pizzas were excellent. &ndash; <a href="http://bit.ly/abqkoF">JAGIN, TripAdvisor</a></li>\r\n<li>&hellip;there is something remarkable here and that is their home made honey/pepper thick cut bacon. Truly a Texas treasure and they sell it by the pound too! &ndash; <a href="http://bit.ly/c9zfjf">Tres B., Yelp</a></li>\r\n<li>This is a fun place with lots going on, really good food, friendly waiters and waitresses, and reasonable prices. &ndash; <a href="http://bit.ly/cLd4gC">Carroll S., Insider Pages</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<div id="voice" class="groupon_voice">\r\n<h2><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-size: 10px; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><strong><br /></strong></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 17, 5, 1, 5, '2010-08-20 06:58:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2010-08-23 00:30:00', '<ul>\r\n<li>Limit 2 per person. Limit 1 per table. Dine-in only. Not valid with other offers or specials. Not valid toward alcohol.</li>\r\n<li><a href="http://www.groupon.com/pages/universal-fine-print">See the rules</a><span> that apply to all deals.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '<ul>\r\n<li>Wide variety of fresh dishes</li>\r\n<li>Delicious honey-pepper bacon</li>\r\n<li>Local, family-owned eatery </li>\r\n<li>Family