(179, '2010-08-31 05:37:42', '2010-08-31 05:37:42', 1, '$10 for $20 Worth of Casual Cuisine and Drinks at Jeffrey''s Café & Wine Bar', '$10-for-$20-worth-of-casual-cuisine-and-drinks-at-jeffrey-s-café-wine-bar', NULL, '<p>To make un-fine wine, simply place grapes beneath a silk pillow, repeatedly mash your head against it, and then wring the pillowcase into a nearby mouth. Taste traditionally produced fine wines with today&rsquo;s Groupon: for $10, you get $20 worth of casual cuisine and drinks at&nbsp;<a href="http://www.jeffreyscafe.com/">Jeffrey''s Caf&eacute; &amp; Wine Bar</a>, located in the heart of Crestwood.</p>\r\n<p>Jeffrey''s&nbsp;<a href="http://www.jeffreyscafe.com/menu.html">menu</a>&nbsp;supplies an abundant selection of fine wines, specialty martinis, satisfying munchies, and tummy-warming coffees and teas. Appease anticipatory palates with a glass of&nbsp;<a href="http://www.jeffreyscafe.com/white_wine.html">white wine</a>&nbsp;($7.50&ndash;$9.50) before inviting your lumberjack date to share a mound of loaded nachos, a festive ensemble of cheddar, peppers, tomatoes, onions, sour cream, and salsa ($9.95). The Diablo sandwich will bring devilish carnivores to their prayin'' knees with swiss, salami, grilled red onion, red and green bell peppers, jalape&ntilde;os, dijon, and mayo ($7.95/$5.75). Head to Jeffrey''s after a tiring night shift at the socializing and dancing factory and get a breakfast wrap, which introduces two poached eggs to a social network of diced tomatoes, peppers, mushrooms, and cheddar ($7.25). Those looking to get their daily surge of caffeine will want to try one of Jeffrey''s&nbsp;<a href="http://www.jeffreyscafe.com/coffees_and_teas.html">coffees or teas</a>, such as the caf&eacute; caramel, a latte with added caramel syrup and whipped cream ($3.50&ndash;$4.40), or the River Valley Fog, a simplistically tasty treat of steamed milk with your pick of flavour shot ($3.35&ndash;$4.30).</p>', '$10 for $20 Worth of Casual Cuisine and Drinks at Jeffrey''s Café & Wine Bar', 10.00, 4.50, 0, '2010-08-31 05:37:59', '2010-09-06 23:30:00', 55.00, 5.50, 5.50, 50, 120, 42543, 53, '<p>Jeffrey''s cozy space is adorned with deep-blue walls, bright and abundant artwork, and comfy seating, all of which contribute to its updated, casual feel.&nbsp;<a href="http://www.jeffreyscafe.com/upcoming.html">Live music</a>&nbsp;from the city''s most prominent artists is often featured (cover charges may apply), allowing aural orifices to take in something other than the screeching oo''s and ahh''s typically associated with wine enjoyment.</p>\r\n<p><em>This deal is only valid for food and drink and cannot be used for cover charges.</em></p>', 0, 0, 1, 5, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2010-09-14 21:30:00', '<ul>\r\n<li>Limit 1 per person, may buy 2 additional as gifts. Limit 1 per table, 2 per table of 6 or more. No cash back. Not valid with other offers. Tax and gratuity not included.</li>\r\n<li><span>&nbsp;that apply to all deals.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '<ul>\r\n<li>Live music from local acts</li>\r\n<li>Fine wine and martinis</li>\r\n<li>Light, casual fare</li>\r\n<li>Coffees, teas, and warm drinks</li>\r\n</ul>', '<h3><a href="http://www.groupon.com/groupon_says/groupon-says-26273441-40541604">How to Properly Taste Wine</a></h3>\r\n<p>For total wine enjoyment, the wine drinker must engage in a multi-step process designed to enhance the flavour, the body, and the unique characteristics with each sip:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Give the wine in your glass one of three names: "Gary," "Darryl," or "Garryl."</li>\r\n<li>Bring the wine glass to your right eye and stare deeply into it for at least 30 minutes until you can no longer tell where the wine ends and you begin.</li>\r\n<li>Starting with your left pinky and moving right, fully submerge each of your fingers into the wine glass until all fingers are in the glass.</li>\r\n<li>Take a sip and slosh it around. When someone gives you some surprising news, spit it out.</li>\r\n<li>Put all the wine from your glass into your mouth, but don''t swallow. When all the wine is in there, open your mouth and say, "Keys. Once angry keeping flagrant." Enjoy the wine that is left in your mouth.</li>\r\n</ol>', 0, 1, 0, 7, 2.00, 3.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'Wine', '', 'http://bit.ly/9pvN5y', 'http://bit.ly/aKCYvL'),
