(371, '2010-10-20 05:45:55', '2010-10-20 05:45:55', 1, ' $25 for $52 Worth of New American Food at Two Rows Classic Grille in Allen', '$25-for-$52-worth-of-new-american-food-at-two-rows-classic-grille-in-allen-8', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>When someone''s getting all up in your grill, the best thing to say is "You better step off! The surface temperature of grills can approach 550 degrees Fahrenheit&mdash;you shouldn''t be standing on that thing!" Today''s deal demonstrates a high regard for safety by leaving the grilling to the professionals: for $10, you get $20 worth of grilled eats, new American food, and more at Two Rows Classic Grille, located in Allen. Per state law, today''s Groupon is not valid for alcohol purchases.</p>\r\n<p>Family owned, Two Rows Classic Grille synthesizes savory edibles fresh and from scratch in a casual dining and imbibing environment. A sundry selection of creative plates don the <a href="http://tworows.com/pdf/new_Two_Rows_Menu_20x15.pdf">menu</a>, including offerings of grilled meats, sandwiches, pastas, Tex-Mex fare, and brick-oven gourmet pizzas. A starter of fried pickle chips, lightly battered and Cajun-dusted, tickles tongues with delightful dill ($6.79), while the brew house fries ($6.99) reunite displaced fried potatoes with old cheddar and chive chums. Two Rows'' hearty entrees represent the finest tastes of our ecosystem: the piquant sashimi tuna ($12.99) reps the surf, the hickory-smoked honey-glazed pork ribs ($12.99 small rack, $18.99 large) oversee the turf, and the chicken-fried steak ($9.99) upholds the territories of Smurf. Pigthusiasts can also appreciate the porcine polish of a cheddar and honey-pepper bacon burger ($8.29). Cap off a committed consumption session with the pineapple and raisin bread pudding ($4.29).</p>\r\n<p>Friendly, attentive servers constantly roam the floor at Two Rows, mirroring the tender care the restaurant exudes toward its <a href="http://tworows.com/community/index.php">community</a> endeavors. Step inside the welcoming, laid-back grillery for grillicious grill fare, without ever having to deplete your home charcoal silo.</p>', '', 10.00, 5.50, 0, '2010-10-20 05:46:16', '2010-10-21 10:45:33', 45.00, 4.50, 4.50, 30, 120, 42464, 53, '<div class="page_content clearfix">\r\n<div class="article description">\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><a href="http://bit.ly/abqkoF">TripAdvisors</a> give Two Rows Classic Grille an average of 3.5 owl eyes. <a href="http://bit.ly/9MGoHI">Yelpers</a> give the restaurant a 3.5-star average, and five <a href="http://bit.ly/cLd4gC">Insider Pagers</a> give the it a three-star average:</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The gourmet brick oven pizzas were excellent. &ndash; <a href="http://bit.ly/abqkoF">JAGIN, TripAdvisor</a></li>\r\n<li>&hellip;there is something remarkable here and that is their home made honey/pepper thick cut bacon. Truly a Texas treasure and they sell it by the pound too! &ndash; <a href="http://bit.ly/c9zfjf">Tres B., Yelp</a></li>\r\n<li>This is a fun place with lots going on, really good food, friendly waiters and waitresses, and reasonable prices. &ndash; <a href="http://bit.ly/cLd4gC">Carroll S., Insider Pages</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<div id="voice" class="groupon_voice">\r\n<h2><span style="font-size: x-small;"><span style="font-size: 10px; font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><strong><br /></strong></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 0, 0, 1, 5, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2010-10-30 18:30:00', '<ul>\r\n<li>Limit 2 per person. Limit 1 per table. Dine-in only. Not valid with other offers or specials. Not valid toward alcohol.</li>\r\n<li><a href="http://www.groupon.com/pages/universal-fine-print">See the rules</a><span> that apply to all deals.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '<ul>\r\n<li>Wide variety of fresh dishes</li>\r\n<li>Delicious honey-pepper bacon</li>\r\n<li>Local, family-owned eatery </li>\r\n<li>Family friendly</li>\r\n<li>Kids menu</li>\r\n</ul>', '<div class="page_content clearfix">\r\n<div class="article description">\r\n<div id="voice" class="groupon_voice">\r\n<h2><span style="font-size: 12px;"><a href="http://www.groupon.com/groupon_says/campaign-groupon-say-0-13424">America''s Youngest Letter</a></span></h2>\r\n<div class="groupon_voice_top">\r\n<p>The letter&nbsp;<em>e</em>&nbsp;is America''s youngest letter, first incorporated in the mid-19th century some 2,600 years after the rest of the Latin alphabet.&nbsp;<em>E</em>&nbsp;quickly rocketed into regular use and in no time was named "America''s Best Letter" in a poll of landowning children who previously could not have even formed the words comprising that title. To capitalize on the letter''s popularity, numerous words added the in-demand grapheme in unnecessary ways, leading to spellings such as "olde," "grille," and "floccinaucinihilipilificatione."</p>\r\n<p><em>E</em>&nbsp;also allowed for the development of the past tense by adding the suffix "-ed" to many verbs. Before this breakthrough, discussion and even thoughts of the past were linguistically impossible, and repeating past mistakes, specifically electing horses to office, was unavoidable.</p>\r\n<p>If you are a quick study, you may have noticed that the previous paragraph has an atypical feature: none of the words contain the letter&nbsp;<em>e</em>. If you take the time to look, you''ll find this isn''t true.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 0, 0, 0, 7, 0.00, 8.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'food ', '', 'http://bit.ly/aIYrBn', 'http://bit.ly/cjkqvW'),
(372, '2010-10-20 05:47:36', '2010-10-21 10:43:31', 1, 'Testovací deal za super cenu', 'testovací-deal-za-super-cenu-1', NULL, '<p>Hubnut&iacute; je st&aacute;le velmi aktu&aacute;ln&iacute; t&eacute;ma. S obezitou m&aacute; probl&eacute;my st&aacute;le v&iacute;ce lid&iacute; po cel&eacute;m světě, a tak se každ&yacute;m dnem objevuje nov&yacute; tip na zhubnut&iacute;. V USA nyn&iacute; zaž&iacute;v&aacute; naprost&yacute; boom bezlepkov&aacute; dieta. Drž&iacute; ji nejen celebrity jako Gwyneth Paltrowov&aacute;, ale v&scaron;ichni, kdo v Americe něco znamenaj&iacute;, např&iacute;klad i svatebn&iacute; dort Chelsey Clintonov&eacute; byl upečen&yacute; bez lepku.</p>', '', 1000.00, 500.00, 0, '2010-10-20 05:48:00', '2010-10-21 10:45:33', 50.00, 499.00, 500.00, 20, 5000, 42621, 56, '<p>Bezlepkov&aacute; dieta&nbsp;je tedy v USA stejn&yacute;m hitem jako před deseti lety&nbsp;snižov&aacute;n&iacute; př&iacute;jmu uhlovodanů. Propaguj&iacute; ji ultrahuben&eacute; herečky a v obchodech se objevuje st&aacute;le v&iacute;ce v&yacute;robků od těstovin, su&scaron;enek, cere&aacute;li&iacute; až po pivo,&nbsp;upozorňuj&iacute;c&iacute; na ten fakt, že jsou bez lepku.</p>\r\n<p>Odborn&iacute;ci si&nbsp;tento boom nedok&aacute;ž&iacute; zcela zdůvodnit, jelikož na rozd&iacute;l od jin&yacute;ch stravovac&iacute;ch bub&aacute;ků, jako jsou třeba trans-tuky, konzumace lepku v podstatě &scaron;kodliv&aacute; nen&iacute;. Jen mal&eacute; procento lid&iacute; nesnese tenhle protein, kter&yacute; se přirozeně vyskytuje v p&scaron;enici, ječmenu a žitě.</p>', 1, 0, 1, 10, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2010-10-30 18:30:00', '<h4>Touha po potravin&aacute;ch bez lepku narůst&aacute;</h4>\r\n<p>Lepek č&aacute;st lid&iacute; nesn&aacute;&scaron;&iacute;, předev&scaron;&iacute;m pak ti, kdo trp&iacute; celiaki&iacute;. Ov&scaron;em celiaků s imunitn&iacute; reakc&iacute; na potraviny obsahuj&iacute;c&iacute; lepek je v americk&eacute; populaci m&eacute;ně než jedno procento. Č&aacute;st dal&scaron;&iacute;ch lid&iacute; pak m&aacute; v&iacute;ce nebo m&eacute;ně v&aacute;žnou alergii či citlivost na lepek; podle doktora Alessia Fasana, ředitele Střediska pro v&yacute;zkum celiakie při Marylandsk&eacute; univerzitě m&aacute; nějak&yacute; druh citlivosti na lepek až sedm nebo osm procent Američanů.</p>', '<h4>Neexistuje ž&aacute;dn&eacute; vědeck&eacute; vysvětlen&iacute;</h4>\r\n<p>Proč lid&eacute; tvrd&iacute;, že se po bezlepkov&eacute; dietě c&iacute;t&iacute; l&iacute;p, nen&iacute; &uacute;plně jasn&eacute; a př&iacute;činy mohou b&yacute;t nepř&iacute;m&eacute;. Ti, kdo eliminuj&iacute; lepkov&eacute; potraviny, mohou zač&iacute;t konzumovat v&iacute;c zemědělsk&yacute;ch produktů a t&iacute;m celkově zač&iacute;t j&iacute;st zdravěji, m&iacute;n&iacute; Dee Sandquistov&aacute;, mluvč&iacute; americk&eacute; dietetick&eacute; asociace.</p>', '<h4>Odborn&iacute;ci varuj&iacute; před drastick&yacute;mi dietami</h4>\r\n<p>Lid&eacute; by si měli uvědomit, že ceny bezlepkov&yacute;ch potravin jsou velmi drah&eacute;. Může to tedy&nbsp;sv&aacute;dět k tomu, že lid&eacute; začnou j&iacute;st buď zcela minim&aacute;lně a nebo jen v&yacute;živově velmi chudou stravu. Což je samozřejmě z pohledu odborn&iacute;ků na v&yacute;živu velmi &scaron;patn&eacute;.</p>', 0, 0, 0, 7, 0.00, 30.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, 'super deal', 'deal, super, bezva, groupon', 'http://bit.ly/aIzsdp', 'http://bit.ly/cg9WLA'),
