(387, '2010-10-23 16:51:18', '2010-10-24 01:10:57', 1, '$60 for a Surfing Lesson from Malibu Surf Shack ($125 Value)', '$60-for-a-surfing-lesson-from-malibu-surf-shack-($125-value)', NULL, '<p>Herbert Hoover won Americans&rsquo; hearts and votes when he promised a college-educated chicken in every pot and a surf board in every garage. Get a taste of the American dream with today''s Groupon: for $60, you get a 1.5-hour surfing lesson from<a href="http://www.malibusurfshack.com/">Malibu Surf Shack</a>&nbsp;(a $125 value) in&nbsp;<a href="http://bit.ly/d0YKOR">Malibu Beach</a>. Additionally, Groupon customers get $60 toward the purchase of a new surfboard.</p>\r\n<p>Prospective oceanographers will get to behold the sights, sounds, and underwater empire of super-intelligent sea turtles along Malibu''s Surfrider Beach. A professional, buoyant instructor will lead the way and provide a steady flow of surfing tips and fun facts. Students are limited to three per instructor, ensuring a high level of personal attention. Surfboards and wetsuits are also included, so prospective wave tamers won''t have to worry about cobbling together a makeshift board out of popsicle sticks, Laffy Taffy, and wishful thinking.</p>\r\n<p>Malibu Surf Shack has been&nbsp;<a href="http://www.malibusurfshack.com/rentals.html">renting</a>&nbsp;surf boards and wetsuits to experienced wave-rodeo enthusiasts and fledgling ten hangers since 1972. A friendly, down-to-earth staff exemplifies the region''s passion for surfing, particularly in the patient way staff members smile through endless&nbsp;<em>Point Break</em>&nbsp;references. With a shop overlooking scenic Surfrider Beach, it&rsquo;s a bodacious place to start learning the basics of surfery or to commence an arduous 11-month voyage to Japan via your cardboard submarine. Malibu Surf Shack offers multiple classes daily, starting at 10 a.m. and running throughout the day. Call to reserve a spot.</p>', '', 125.00, 60.00, 0, '2010-10-23 18:30:00', '2010-10-24 18:35:01', 52.00, 65.00, 65.00, 1, NULL, 42557, 56, '', 1, 0, 1, 1, '2010-10-24 01:44:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2010-11-29 18:30:00', '<ul>\r\n<li>Expires Jun 15, 2011</li>\r\n<li>Limit 1 per person, may buy multiple as gifts.&nbsp;<strong>Must be 5 or older</strong>. By appointment only; subject to availability. Not valid with other offers.</li>\r\n</ul>', '', '', 1, 1, 1, 6, 0.00, 50.00, 30.00, 60.00, 0.00, '', '', 'http://bit.ly/ag0ujM', 'http://bit.ly/cVE0lE'),
