(429, '2010-11-02 08:30:09', '2010-11-02 18:45:33', 1, '$20 for $50 Worth of Needlepoint Belts and More ', '$20-for-$50-worth-of-needlepoint-belts-and-more', NULL, '<p>Before the invention of belts, pants were held up by snakes worn as suspenders, wishful thinking, or omnipresent indentured servants paying off gambling debts. Enjoy the self-contained propping up of pants with today''s Groupon: for $20, you get $50 worth of needlepoint belts and more at <a href="http://www.tuckerblair.com/home.html">Tucker Blair</a>. This Groupon can only be redeemed online.</p>\r\n<p>Tucker Blair''s needlepoint <a href="http://store.tuckerblair.com/product-belts.html">belts</a> are tightly hand-stitched with 100% wool yarn onto bands of high-quality full-grain leather. Go black-tie casual with a <a href="http://store.tuckerblair.com/bowties.html">bow tie and champagne</a> belt ($55), or bring some holiday cheer to your belt loops with a <a href="http://store.tuckerblair.com/snowmen.html">snowman</a> design ($88). Tucker Blair belts are an ideal way to proclaim one''s enthusiasm for <a href="http://bit.ly/cBLGEW">lacrosse</a>, <a href="http://store.tuckerblair.com/golf.html">golf</a>, and <a href="http://store.tuckerblair.com/crabbeerbottle.html">libation crustaceans</a> ($88 each). The company frequently puts a stitchy spin on new products, branching into legal-in-kangaroo-boxing above-the-belt territory with <a href="http://store.tuckerblair.com/product-classic-chatham-polo.html">classic Chatham polos</a> available in myriad colors ($39.50 each).</p>', '', 50.00, 20.00, 0, '2010-11-01 18:30:00', '2010-11-03 18:30:00', 60.00, 30.00, 30.00, 9, 15, 42464, 59, '<p>Tucker Blair has received multiple mentions from the <a href="http://content.tuckerblair.com/">press</a> including features in <a href="http://nymag.com/daily/fashion/2009/12/if_you_thought_vineyard_vines.html"><em>New York</em> magazine</a> and <a href="http://www.thrillist.com/washington-dc/tucker-blair">Thrillist</a>:</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>But sometimes a brand so special comes along, we have to do a little something extra. And so we would like to introduce you to Tucker Blair, which has been pushing their Frosty Needlepoint Belt on us. We did a little research to find out more about what appeared to be this prestigious, august label, and it turns out, its beginnings were impossibly humble &ndash; <a href="http://nymag.com/daily/fashion/2009/12/if_you_thought_vineyard_vines.html">Amy Odell, <em>New York</em></a></li>\r\n<li>Blair''s a DC-based e-purveyor of needlepoint accessories for the jauntily self-assured, whose page-long mission statement kicks off with the above soul-searcher, then moves on to weighty subjects from "Nauset Beach", to "Colgate", to "strolling". &ndash; <a href="http://www.thrillist.com/washington-dc/tucker-blair">Thrillist</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</blockquote>', 1, 0, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-03-07 18:30:00', '<h3>The Fine Print</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Expires in 1 year</li>\r\n<li>Limit 2 per person, may buy multiple as gifts. Limit 1 per order. No cash back. Shipping not included.</li>\r\n<li><a href="http://www.groupon.com/pages/universal-fine-print">See the rules</a><span> that apply to all deals.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '<ul>\r\n<li>Redeem online</li>\r\n<li>Creative needlepoint belts</li>\r\n<li>100% wool &amp; quality leather</li>\r\n<li>Classic polo shirts</li>\r\n</ul>', '', 0, 1, 0, 7, 0.00, 50.00, 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '', '', 'http://bit.ly/9D9me3', 'http://bit.ly/cdbX6L'),
