(727, '2011-01-11 01:16:00', '2011-01-12 12:30:24', 1, '$13 Admission to the Jazz Club Tour on Sept. 1 from the Jazz Institute of Chicago ($30 Value)', '$13-admission-to-the-jazz-club-tour-on-sept.-1-from-the-jazz-institute-of-chicago-($30-value)-1', NULL, '<div class="article description">\r\n<p><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman''; font-size: 16px;">\r\n<div style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; background-image: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: #ffffff; background-position: initial initial; margin: 8px;">\r\n<div class="article description">\r\n<p>For $13, today''s side deal gets you admission to this year''s jazz club tour from the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.jazzinchicago.org/presents/jazz-club-tour">Jazz Institute of Chicago</a>&nbsp;on Wednesday, September 1 (a $30 value). The tour kicks off at 7 p.m. and can be as long or as short as you want it to be.</p>\r\n<p>The Jazz Club Tour provides access to 13 participating jazz clubs around Chicago, a city known for its history with and affinity for jazz music. After purchasing today''s Groupon, you''ll be sent a packet with a letter, a map of all participating clubs, and a button to wear that will act as your all-access pass for the evening. Enjoy music, drinks, and convivial good times everywhere from&nbsp;<a href="http://www.buddyguys.com/">Buddy Guy''s Legends</a>&nbsp;in the South Loop and&nbsp;<a href="http://www.redpepperslounge.com/">Red Pepper''s Masquerade Lounge</a>&nbsp;on 87th Street to the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.greenmilljazz.com/">Green Mill</a>&nbsp;in Uptown. The Chicago Trolley Company will provide door-to-door transportation between clubs, making the experience safe and stress-free for everyone involved. Some of the proceeds from the tour will go to benefit the Jazz Institute of Chicago, which provides free concerts all year round, including the Chicago Jazz Festival, which takes flight one week after the tour.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>', '', 30.00, 15.00, 0, '2011-01-11 01:16:00', '2011-01-12 11:00:00', 50.00, 15.00, 15.00, 4, 1000, 42563, 172, '<div class="article description">\r\n<p>For $13, today''s side deal gets you admission to this year''s jazz club tour from the <a href="http://www.jazzinchicago.org/presents/jazz-club-tour">Jazz Institute of Chicago</a> on Wednesday, September 1 (a $30 value). The tour kicks off at 7 p.m. and can be as long or as short as you want it to be.</p>\r\n<p>The Jazz Club Tour provides access to 13 participating jazz clubs around Chicago, a city known for its history with and affinity for jazz music. After purchasing today''s Groupon, you''ll be sent a packet with a letter, a map of all participating clubs, and a button to wear that will act as your all-access pass for the evening. Enjoy music, drinks, and convivial good times everywhere from <a href="http://www.buddyguys.com/">Buddy Guy''s Legends</a> in the South Loop and <a href="http://www.redpepperslounge.com/">Red Pepper''s Masquerade Lounge</a> on 87th Street to the <a href="http://www.greenmilljazz.com/">Green Mill</a> in Uptown. The Chicago Trolley Company will provide door-to-door transportation between clubs, making the experience safe and stress-free for everyone involved. Some of the proceeds from the tour will go to benefit the Jazz Institute of Chicago, which provides free concerts all year round, including the Chicago Jazz Festival, which takes flight one week after the tour.</p>\r\n</div>', 5, 0, 1, NULL, '2011-01-12 11:06:30', '2011-01-12 12:00:00', '2011-01-30 18:30:00', '<p>Limit 6 per person. Must provide shipping address at check-out. No exchanges or refunds.</p>', '<ul>\r\n<li>Visit 13 jazz clubs</li>\r\n<li>Trolley service between stops </li>\r\n<li>Proceeds benefit the Jazz Institute of Chicago</li>\r\n</ul>', '<div class="article description">\r\n<p>For $13, today''s side deal gets you admissio